gui_close_cell_view(25.10)                          gui_close_cell_view(25.10)

Name
       gui_close_cell_view - Closes the Cell Viewer

Syntax
       gui_close_cell_view [-help]

       Closes the Cell Viewer.

       If the Cell Viewer is open at any stage of the design flow, you can use
       the gui_close_cell_view command to close it.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the gui_close_cell_view command.

              For  a detailed description of the command, use the man command:
              man gui_close_cell_view.

Related Information
              * gui_open_cell_view

              * Tools Menu chapter of the Menu Reference

                * Cell Viewer

